    public abstract class DtoFieldSetService<T extends AbstractDto>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FieldSetService<T>
    Service class that handles Dto updates based on a Map containing the key "placement.[field]" or "[field]" and the value in the map being the value that field should be updated to. Examples: "placement.approvingClientContactID":"12345" or "approvingClientContactID":"12345" will update approvingClientContactID to 12345 on the PlacementDto.
